{"tid":2448101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟反擊英國 德國法國意大利都暫停注射阿斯利康疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-15T16:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T03:58:16.000Z","uid":13745,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e84966c71c5bbcf0f2cbdf0c5e30116b75df5b75","tid":2448101,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2383099&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7b2f23d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383099</a><br />\n<br />\n繼德國後，法國及意大利都宣布停用英國阿斯利康新冠疫苗。法國總統馬克龍宣布，會在24小時內停用阿斯利康疫苗。意大利藥管部門就說衹是預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n德國衛生部表示，是鑑於最新有關接種阿斯利康疫苗後出現血栓塞個案，決定暫停使用這款疫苗，衛生部指只是預防措施，會對相關病例進一步調查。衛生部又指，歐洲藥品管理局將決定最新資訊會否及如何影響疫苗批准使用。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭、荷蘭、奧地利、愛沙尼亞、丹麥和挪威等歐洲國家，日前已暫停為民眾接種阿斯利康疫苗。英國就表明會繼續為民眾打阿斯利康疫苗。"},{"pid":"9010ba407481bb03ecbeea757e3b9f33c988fbd6","tid":2448101,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2022738/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2022738%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=1ae74a76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F2022738%2F&h=422a0bfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/2022738/</a><br />\n南韓自上月開始疫苗接種計劃後，已有588958人接種疫苗，至今有16宗死亡個案，當局經調查後表示，其中14與疫苗無直接關係。而8520宗懷疑異常反應個案中，接近99%是阿斯利康疫苗。"},{"pid":"d0279886ae5bbe5f4244531af0b8e48126680bbe","tid":2448101,"uid":24966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"秦國都禁喇 唔通學科興咁死人都照打咩"},{"pid":"5148fd4c620434d700fb2c034b93ab8bbf0d51ac","tid":2448101,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d0279886ae5bbe5f4244531af0b8e48126680bbe","tid":2448101,"uid":24966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"秦國都禁喇 唔通學科興咁死人都照打咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"但係英國都照打喎<br />\n重話佢有效添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3433cbee84f13b346c1c2f532a68d80fd18dfc64","tid":2448101,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-23/540325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-23%2F540325&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=2e433622\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-23/540325</a><br />\n<br />\n疫苗抗疫捷報頻傳! 全球感染人數緩減 英國死亡數下降64%"},{"pid":"251135b3ea76c7897a1619a64f03f1d7ab444977","tid":2448101,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"一開始唔係為咗爭疫苗禁止佢係荷蘭間廠運啲疫苗返英國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacbcaa290dbc89703e4b10072f1bc6cde863946","tid":2448101,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"歐盟想呃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9030f3bfcaebdadf9c1d850d24f6d33f1d5d72","tid":2448101,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T19:48:14.000Z","msg":"個個國家玩內循環，玩唔掂果個又會開始撩交打，WW3不完了"},{"pid":"805df131b0f2ce1ee8165a7a65f24bbb9c1cd9c9","tid":2448101,"uid":75406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"世衛講既野咁熟口面既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df58296fd77b3489c0d66f151ab2e9d4d49036ab","tid":2448101,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\